snippet.title: Audio reveals Johnny Depp told Amber Heard, 'We are a crime scene waiting to happen'
snippet.description:
Extracts of a tape recording of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard discussing physical violence in their relationship which has been released by the Crown Prosecution Service. The audio also captured a discussion the two had over an altercation in the bathroom
